name: Ego Mortem
description:
Some may relate the end of life to the death of the ego, but the cemeteries are there to show us that this is not the case. the structure of the tombs and the layout of the tombs are minutely thought out by the living, to always remind us of capital power

This cave has a privileged place inside the cemetery, with underground carneira, carved from a beautiful stone and with a metal sculpture with more than a meter of Jesus sitting above the bodies, found on municipal graveyard of São Francisco/Curitiba

photogrammetry scan/ 2021 - Higor Casagrande
